Smeet is a browser-based 2.5D computer graphics social network, developed by Smeet Communications GmbH based in Berlin, Germany. The company was founded in 2007 by Burckhardt Bonello and Philipp Boutellier and is managed by Sebastian Funke (CEO), Daniel Bülhoff (COO) and Reinhard Köhn (CTO). Smeet creates virtual worlds in which people can meet and interact with their avatars. Smeet combines casual and social gaming.
